m\": 1419, \"to\": 1426}, {\"ngram\": \"the age\", \"from\": 1440, \"to\": 1447}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Nicole also reflected on filming one specific scene with her ex in the psychological drama.\", \"from\": 1464, \"to\": 1555, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Nicole\", \"from\": 1464, \"to\": 1470}, {\"ngram\": \"one specific scene\", \"from\": 1497, \"to\": 1515}, {\"ngram\": \"her ex\", \"from\": 1521, \"to\": 1527}, {\"ngram\": \"the psychological drama\", \"from\": 1531, \"to\": 1554}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It was the scene with Tom and I where I start by smoking the spliff in bed and where I laugh and deliver the long monologue,\\\" she recalled.\", \"from\": 1556, \"to\": 1696, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the scene\", \"from\": 1564, \"to\": 1573}, {\"ngram\": \"Tom\", \"from\": 1579, \"to\": 1582}, {\"ngram\": \"the spliff\", \"from\": 1614, \"to\": 1624}, {\"ngram\": \"bed\", \"from\": 1628, \"to\": 1631}, {\"ngram\": \"the long monologue\", \"from\": 1662, \"to\": 1680}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"That took many weeks.\", \"from\": 1697, \"to\": 1719, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"many weeks\", \"from\": 1708, \"to\": 1718}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A lot of that was rehearsing in the bedroom and then him not liking what we'd done.\", \"from\": 1720, \"to\": 1803, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A lot\", \"from\": 1720, \"to\": 1725}, {\"ngram\": \"the bedroom\", \"from\": 1752, \"to\": 1763}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So we ended up reworking it, constructing it as we went along.\", \"from\": 1804, \"to\": 1866, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"There was no need to rush.\", \"from\": 1867, \"to\": 1893, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"no need\", \"from\": 1877, \"to\": 1884}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Stanley would never go over budget.\", \"from\": 1894, \"to\": 1929, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Stanley\", \"from\": 1894, \"to\": 1901}, {\"ngram\": \"budget\", \"from\": 1922, \"to\": 1928}]}, {\"sentence\": \"What he bought was time.\\\"\", \"from\": 1930, \"to\": 1955, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"time\", \"from\": 1949, \"to\": 1953}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She then explained that the scene evolved under the director's guidance.\", \"from\": 1957, \"to\": 2029, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the scene\", \"from\": 1981, \"to\": 1990}, {\"ngram\": \"the director's guidance\", \"from\": 2005, \"to\": 2028}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Just a lot of talking.\", \"from\": 2030, \"to\": 2053, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\\"Just a lot\", \"from\": 2030, \"to\": 2041}, {\"ngram\": \"talking\", \"from\": 2045, \"to\": 2052}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When Tom and I first started with Stanley, it was at his home, and we did not even go over to the sets at Pinewood [Studios].\", \"from\": 2054, \"to\": 2179, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Tom\", \"from\": 2059, \"to\": 2062}, {\"ngram\": \"Stanley\", \"from\": 2088, \"to\": 2095}, {\"ngram\": \"his home\", \"from\": 2107, \"to\": 2115}, {\"ngram\": \"the sets\", \"from\": 2148, \"to\": 2156}, {\"ngram\": \"Pinewood\", \"from\": 2160, \"to\": 2168}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Six, eight weeks passed, and we are wondering, 'Are we ever going to start?'\", \"from\": 2180, \"to\": 2256, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"eight weeks\", \"from\": 2185, \"to\": 2196}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And we just would not start,\\\" Nicole said.\", \"from\": 2257, \"to\": 2299, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Nicole\", \"from\": 2287, \"to\": 2293}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We were getting comfortable with each other, comfortable enough to throw out ideas.\", \"from\": 2300, \"to\": 2384, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"ideas\", \"from\": 2378, \"to\": 2383}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For that scene, we improvised the beginning of it through the rehearsals.\\\"\", \"